```ts title="docusaurus.config.js"
export default {
  plugins: [
    [
      'rsdoctor',
      {
        /* options */
      },
    ],
  ],
};
```

:::tip

Turn it on conditionally, based on an environment variable:

```ts title="docusaurus.config.js"
export default {
  plugins: [
    process.env.RSDOCTOR === 'true' && [
      'rsdoctor',
      {
        /* options */
      },
    ],
  ],
};
```

```bash
# Build without Rsdoctor
npm run build

# Build with Rsdoctor
RSDOCTOR=true npm run build
```

:::

